  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of the study is whether subjects with hypertension and proteinuria
      display increased sympathetic nerve activity compared to hypertensive subjects without
      proteinuria and normotensive controls.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
